maltcms.commands.fragments.visualization
Class ChromatogramVisualizer

java.lang.Object
  cross.commands.fragments.AFragmentCommand
      maltcms.commands.fragments.visualization.ChromatogramVisualizer
All Implemented Interfaces:
IFragmentCommand, ICommand<TupleND<IFileFragment>,TupleND<IFileFragment>>, IWorkflowElement, IEventSource<IWorkflowResult>, IConfigurable, IXMLSerializable
public class ChromatogramVisualizer
extends AFragmentCommand

Visualizes a chromatogram as a heat map, based on the empirical distribution of intensity values, using a user defined sample model and color model.

Author:
Nils.Hoffmann@cebitec.uni-bielefeld.de
